      "text": "「それは自分を魅力的に見せるポーズで\nファッションをアピールするポーズじゃない！」って",
      "startTime": 236.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui026.m4a",
      "text": "ファッションショーは服が主役なのに\n私は服よりも自分が目立とうとしてしまった……",
      "startTime": 243.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui027.m4a",
      "text": "最初から私は何もかも間違っていたんです！",
      "startTime": 248.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（今までの経験が通用しなかったことが）\n（そんなにショックだったのか……）",
      "startTime": 255.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui028.m4a",
      "text": "何より悔しかったのは「TRINITYAiLEも\n大したことないわね」と笑われたことです",
      "startTime": 261.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui029.m4a",
      "text": "私が悪く言われるのは構いません\n私の努力が足りなかったのは事実ですから",
      "startTime": 269.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui030.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そのせいでトリエルまで……優やすみれまで\nそう見られるのは我慢出来ません！",
      "startTime": 277.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_02-rui031.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルのリーダーとしてこのままでは終われません！\nお願いします、私の練習時間を倍にして下さい！",
      "startTime": 285.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
